cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.SI

The paper proposes a new algorithm for recommender systems that combines probabilistic matrix factorization (PMF) and topic modeling (e.g., LDA). This makes it likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper deals with online learning, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
